plot: Jerry Seinfeld and Superman hang out in Manhattan, comically chatting about everything from restaurant reservations to the essence of being the Man of Steel. But not even Superman can completely save the day when Jerry's DVD player gets stolen. Fortunately, it was purchased on a certain credit card...   Written by  mooveeguy
